ave been licensed by the library or reserved under law. The BYU Copyright Licensing Office has created a webpage about <a href="http://lib.byu.edu/sites/copyright/about-copyright/copyright-desicions/" title="Copyright Decisions">Copyright Decisions</a> that is helpful in answering some of these questions.&nbsp; The information provided offers you some tips on when works can be used lawfully in your teaching without requesting permission or incurring additional cost.</div>
